snippet.title: Short Trailer | Quiz Realm
snippet.description:
Quizrealm represents a completely new way for streamers to interact with chat. The quiz show consists of different types of quizzes for which different predefined or self-made question sets can be used. Depending on the quiz type the streamer duels against his chat or other streamers and can prove his knowledge.


Try it out now and for more information/registration visit our Discord at endrealm.net/discord.

The video shows the A-Version of the game.
